   "end": "6.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.120", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.480", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fotografen der Agentur Reuters haben dieser Tage einen Pulitzer-Preis gewonnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.120", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie dokumentieren mit schockierenden Bildern das Elend der muslimischen Minderheit der Rohingya auf der Flucht nach Bangladesch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.440", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Bilder f\u00fchren uns das furchtbare Grauen der Vertreibung von 700\u00a0000\u00a0Kindern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.080", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frauen und M\u00e4nnern vor Augen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.400", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihre Angst und ihre Verzweiflung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Bilder k\u00f6nnen niemanden kaltlassen au\u00dfer Sie von der AfD."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.080", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie macht Ihr Hass blind f\u00fcr die Realit\u00e4t."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.520", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "K\u00fcrzlich haben die Vereinten Nationen Myanmar auf die sogenannte Liste der Schande gesetzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.240", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Liste der Staaten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.000", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen sexuelle Gewalt gezielt in bewaffneten Konflikten eingesetzt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.800", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir hier im Bundestag eine Liste der Schande h\u00e4tten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.120", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "st\u00fcnden Ihre Namen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.040", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren von der AfD, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.760", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ganz oben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den humanit\u00e4ren UN-Organisationen und unabh\u00e4ngigen Beobachtern wird seit langem der Zugang in die myanmarische Provinz Rakhine verwehrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.720", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
