   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist eine Region im Dunkeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.480", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist ein Schauplatz von Verbrechen gegen die Menschlichkeit bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.440", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Akten ethnischer S\u00e4uberungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.400", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So sagt es der Hochkommissar f\u00fcr Menschenrechte Seid al-Hussein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.240", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er fragt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.840", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie viel m\u00fcssen Menschen erdulden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.440", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bevor ihr Leid wahrgenommen wird und ihre Identit\u00e4t und ihre Rechte anerkannt werden von ihrer Regierung und von der Welt?\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen ist unsere interfraktionelle Initiative wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.360", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sollte auch Signalwirkung haben,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.320", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr Minderheiten weltweit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.320", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr Opfer staatlicher Willk\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ganz gleich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.880", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welcher Religion oder Weltanschauung sie angeh\u00f6ren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.680", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Deutsche Bundestag das Elend von Ausgegrenzten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verfolgten und Ermordeten in den Fokus nimmt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass thematisiert wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.600", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was nicht nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.400", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
