   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.800", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit diesem Antrag rufen wir in Erinnerung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Rohingya in Myanmar seit Jahren systematisch entrechtet werden und sogar die Bezeichnung \u201eRohingya\u201c verboten ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.040", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir setzen uns f\u00fcr volle b\u00fcrgerliche und politische Rechte der Rohingya ein und daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.640", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie die Staatsangeh\u00f6rigkeit Myanmars bekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.160", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.240", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hilfsorganisationen und unabh\u00e4ngigen Beobachtern muss endlich der Zugang nach Rakhine gew\u00e4hrt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.120", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viertens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.360", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gefl\u00fcchtete k\u00f6nnen nicht zur R\u00fcckkehr in ein Land gezwungen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.720", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem sie erniedrigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.600", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
