   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.480", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine R\u00fcckkehr nach Myanmar darf nur freiwillig erfolgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.440", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sicher und in Begleitung von internationalen Helfern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.240", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcnftens. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.200", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade nach den schrecklichen Erfahrungen von Ruanda und Srebrenica und angesichts schlimmster Kriegsverbrechen in Syrien braucht es eine juristische Aufarbeitung aller in Myanmar begangenen Menschenrechtsverletzungen und die Verurteilung der T\u00e4ter sowie die Entsch\u00e4digung der Opfer."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.640", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.680", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dieser Antrag ist wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.000", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir h\u00e4tten ihn fr\u00fcher zustande bringen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.320", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie h\u00e4tten auch Die Linke einbeziehen k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.960", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen der Gro\u00dfen Koalition. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er k\u00f6nnte zudem noch besser sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.160", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum war es Ihnen nicht m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.840", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
