  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abgeordnete der EVP, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.240", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sozialdemokraten und Liberale im Europaparlament hatten mit dieser berechtigten Forderung kein Problem."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.640", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Angesichts der drohenden Monsunzeit in den Lagern von Bangladesch stellt sich die Frage: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum kann sich unser Parlament nicht konkret auf eine Erh\u00f6hung der Mittel f\u00fcr die humanit\u00e4re Hilfe festlegen und bel\u00e4sst es bei Absichtserkl\u00e4rungen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.880", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies sind kleine Wermutstropfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.920", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichwohl sendet der Bundestag eine unmissverst\u00e4ndliche Botschaft aus: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.880", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Elend der Rohingya geht uns etwas an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.200", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir schauen hin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.120", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben klare politische Forderungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.960", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir fordern die Bundesregierung auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.560", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich zu handeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.200", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.520", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner ist der Kollege Sebastian Brehm, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.960", 
